{"tid":588580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"游蕙禎票倉黃埔東投票率比2016少3%","createTime":"2018-03-11T10:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T10:07:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"868a5308f177d6cd39fe85090aee2a547b4112cd","tid":588580,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/vote311-04_ejxhl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fvote311-04_ejxhl_1200x0.png&h=7be2b233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會補選今日舉行，早上7:30已開始進行投票。今次選舉選前氣氛淡靜，外界指如投票率低，將不利民主派候選人選情。究竟今日投票率如何？《立場新聞》在三區各揀選了焦點票站，全日更新投票率走勢。<br />\n<br />\n其中在九龍西，今次補選議席因青年新政游蕙禎被 DQ 而產生。游蕙禎於 2016 年選舉共得 20,643 票，其票倉主要在她曾任社區主任的黃埔區。她在黃埔東選區得票率為 11.6%，遠高於其九龍西整體得票率 7.4%，亦為眾區之最。今次補選，游蕙禎票倉選區投票率走勢如何？<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎今次以非建制派「最大公約數」自居出戰補選。2016 年立法會選舉，全九龍西最多選民支持非建制的一區，是「南山、大坑東及大坑西」，區議員為民協譚國僑，非建制候選人總得票為建制派的 2.05 倍，為九龍西兩派得票最懸殊一區。今年補選該區的投票率，對反映非建制派支持者投票意欲，有指標性作用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E8%A5%BF%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99-%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E7%8E%87%E8%B5%B0%E5%8B%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A3%259C%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%258D%25B5%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%258E%2587%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%258B%25A2%2F&d=n4LuCQ6OSPaO9li2%2F7zAc9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8ded85b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A3%259C%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%258D%25B5%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%258E%2587%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%258B%25A2%2F&h=0fe4896e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E8%A5%BF%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99-%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E7%8E%87%E8%B5%B0%E5%8B%A2/</a>"}]}